msgid "## 3 Prerequisites"
msgstr "## 3 前提条件"

msgid "### 3.1 Model Weight"
msgstr "### 3.1 模型权重"

msgid ""
"The following model variants are available. It is recommended to download "
"the model weight to a shared directory accessible to all nodes."
msgstr "以下模型变体可用。建议将模型权重下载到所有节点均可访问的共享目录中。"

msgid ""
"| Model                | Hardware Requirement                                                                             | Download                                                                 |\n"
"| -------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------------ |\n"
"| Qwen3-Omni-30B-A3B (BF16) | Atlas 800I A3 (64G, 1\\~2 cards)<br>Atlas 800I A2 (64G, 2\\~4 cards) | [Download](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/Qwen/Qwen3-Omni-30B-A3B)          |\n"
"| Qwen3-Omni-30B-A3B-W8A8   | Atlas 800I A3 (64G, 1\\~2 cards)<br>Atlas 800I A2 (64G, 2\\~4 cards)                               |  N/A|"
msgstr ""
"| 模型                | 硬件要求                                                                             | 下载                                                                 |\n"
"| -------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------------ |\n"
"| Qwen3-Omni-30B-A3B (BF16) | Atlas 800I A3 (64G, 1\\~2 卡)<br>Atlas 800I A2 (64G, 2\\~4 卡) | [下载](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/Qwen/Qwen3-Omni-30B-A3B)          |\n"
"| Qwen3-Omni-30B-A3B-W8A8   | Atlas 800I A3 (64G, 1\\~2 卡)<br>Atlas 800I A2 (64G, 2\\~4 卡)                               |  不适用|"

msgid ""
"The W8A8 quantized weights are not available for direct download, you can "
"obtain them by quantizing the BF16 model using **msmodelslim**. Refer to the"
" [Quantization Guide](../../user_guide/feature_guide/quantization.md) for "
"details. All model paths in this document should be adjusted to your actual "
"local paths."
msgstr ""
"W8A8 量化权重无法直接下载，您可以通过使用 **msmodelslim** 对 BF16 "
"模型进行量化来获取。详情请参考[量化指南](../../user_guide/feature_guide/quantization.md)。本文档中的所有模型路径均应替换为您实际的本地路径。"

msgid ""
"These are the recommended numbers of cards, which can be adjusted according "
"to the actual situation."
msgstr "这些是推荐的卡数，可根据实际情况进行调整。"

msgid ""
"Qwen3-Omni-30B-A3B-W8A8 adopts a hybrid quantization strategy (ordered by "
"model structure):"
msgstr "Qwen3-Omni-30B-A3B-W8A8 采用混合量化策略（按模型结构排序）："

msgid ""
"- **Embedding layer**: BF16 (no quantization)\n"
"    - **Q/K normalization** (q_norm, k_norm): BF16\n"
"    - **Attention projections** (q/k/v/o_proj): Static W8A8 with pre-computed per-tensor scales\n"
"    - **MoE routing gate** (mlp.gate): BF16\n"
"    - **MoE expert projections** (gate/up/down_proj): Dynamic W8A8 where input scales are computed on-the-fly during inference"
msgstr ""
"- **嵌入层**：BF16（未量化）\n"
"    - **Q/K 归一化** (q_norm, k_norm)：BF16\n"
"    - **注意力投影** (q/k/v/o_proj)：静态 W8A8，使用预计算的逐张量缩放因子\n"
"    - **MoE 路由门控** (mlp.gate)：BF16\n"
"    - **MoE 专家投影** (gate/up/down_proj)：动态 W8A8，输入缩放因子在推理过程中实时计算"

msgid ""
"It is recommended to download the model weight to a shared directory across "
"multiple nodes."
msgstr "建议将模型权重下载到跨多个节点的共享目录中。"

