msgid "## 9 Performance Tuning"
msgstr "## 9 性能调优"

msgid "### 9.1 Recommended Configurations"
msgstr "### 9.1 推荐配置"

msgid ""
"> **Note**: The following configurations are validated in specific test "
"environments and are for reference only. The optimal configuration depends "
"on factors such as maximum input/output length, prefix cache hit rate, "
"precision requirements, and deployment machine ratios. It is recommended to "
"refer to Section 9.2 for tuning based on actual conditions."
msgstr ""
"> "
"**注意**：以下配置在特定测试环境中验证，仅供参考。最佳配置取决于最大输入/输出长度、前缀缓存命中率、精度要求及部署机器配比等因素。建议根据实际情况参考第9.2节进行调优。"

msgid "#### Table 1: Scenario Overview"
msgstr "#### 表1：场景概览"

msgid ""
"| Scenario        | Deployment Mode   | *Total NPUs      | Weight Version | Key Considerations                                               |\n"
"| --------------- | ----------------- | ---------------- | -------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| High Throughput | Single-Node (TP1) | 1 (A3)<br>2 (A2) | W8A8           | Single-card deployment maximizes concurrent request processing   |\n"
"| Low Latency     | Single-Node (TP4) | 2 (A3)<br>4 (A2) | W8A8           | Multi-card TP reduces per-token latency with expert parallelism  |\n"
"| Long Context    | Single-Node (TP4) | 2 (A3)<br>4 (A2) | W8A8           | Reduces concurrent sequences to accommodate longer max-model-len |"
msgstr ""
"| 场景            | 部署模式          | *NPU总数         | 权重版本       | 关键考量                                                         |\n"
"| --------------- | ----------------- | ---------------- | -------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| 高吞吐          | 单节点 (TP1)      | 1 (A3)<br>2 (A2) | W8A8           | 单卡部署最大化并发请求处理                                       |\n"
"| 低延迟          | 单节点 (TP4)      | 2 (A3)<br>4 (A2) | W8A8           | 多卡TP通过专家并行降低每token延迟                                |\n"
"| 长上下文        | 单节点 (TP4)      | 2 (A3)<br>4 (A2) | W8A8           | 减少并发序列以容纳更长的max-model-len                            |"

msgid ""
"> `*Total NPUs` indicates the total number of NPUs used across all nodes. On"
" Atlas 800I A3, each NPU contains two dies (chips), so TP4 requires 4 chips "
"= 2 NPUs."
msgstr ""
"> `*NPU总数`表示所有节点使用的NPU总数。在Atlas 800I A3上，每个NPU包含两个die（芯片），因此TP4需要4个芯片=2个NPU。"

msgid "#### Table 2: Detailed Node Configuration"
msgstr "#### 表2：详细节点配置"

msgid ""
"| Scenario        | NPUs   | TP  | max-model-len | max-num-seqs | FUSED_MC2 | EP  | hf-overrides |\n"
"| --------------- | ------ | --- | ------------- | ------------ | --------- | --- | ------------ |\n"
"| High Throughput | 1 (A3) | 1   | 37364         | 100          | Off       | Off | -            |\n"
"| Low Latency     | 2 (A3) | 4   | 37364         | 100          | Off       | On  | -            |\n"
"| Long Context    | 2 (A3) | 4   | 131072        | 14           | Off       | On  | YaRN         |"
msgstr ""
"| 场景            | NPU    | TP  | max-model-len | max-num-seqs | FUSED_MC2 | EP  | hf-overrides |\n"
"| --------------- | ------ | --- | ------------- | ------------ | --------- | --- | ------------ |\n"
"| 高吞吐          | 1 (A3) | 1   | 37364         | 100          | Off       | Off | -            |\n"
"| 低延迟          | 2 (A3) | 4   | 37364         | 100          | Off       | On  | -            |\n"
"| 长上下文        | 2 (A3) | 4   | 131072        | 14           | Off       | On  | YaRN         |"

